description:
This course is designed to assist you to find clarity in creating your dreams and focus in attaining your goal.

This course is 60 minutes long with hideouts, visualization excesses and video and audio presentation. My intention at the end of this course is to guide you to realize your passion and focus in the creation of the life you want. There is a free Ebook handout at the end of this programme.
title: Design The Life You Want. Learn How To Build A Dream Board
